        "action": "Make it illegal for pedestrians to cross a road where a crossing is visible.",
        "additional_details": "",
        "background": "Too many RTA occur on the roads of England, with a majority of these being due to pedestrians crossing a road where a pedestrian crossing is accessible for them to use. Drivers are punished for stupidity of pedestrians! It\u2019s illegal in the USA and I feel it should be here where a crossing is visible",
